title: Average price of cut flowers sold in auctions in the Netherlands 2018 to 2019
yAxis: Average price per flower in eurocent
summary: This is a bar chart representing Month in the x axis and Average price per flower in eurocent in the y axis.
The Average price per flower in eurocent is highest at Month Nov '19 and lowest at Month Jul '18.

max_summary: This bar chart has 20 columns on the x axis representing Month, and Average price per flower in eurocent in each Month on the y axis.

The minimum Month Jul '18 has got 1.71 times less Average price per flower in eurocent than the maximum Month Nov '19.
Average price per flower in eurocent at Month Nov '19 is 36.0 , second place is Dec '18 at 35.0, and thirdly is Dec '18 at 35.0.
The Average price per flower in eurocent has decreased over the past 20 Months.
Month Sep '19, Feb '19, Sep '18, and Jun '18 have a similar Average price per flower in eurocent that is 28.0.
The lowest value 21.0 at Jul '18 is almost 1.25 times smaller than the average value 28.75.
The Average price per flower in eurocent is 575.0 if we add up values of all Months.
